N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4223.11 - Safe keeping of registration certificate

State Regulations

The racing secretary shall be responsible for the safe
keeping of registration certificates and the safe return of same to owners at
the conclusion of the meeting. Notes
